      "para_id": "Q001021.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(Upper Text, 1) Ur-Nanše , king of Lagaš , child of Gunidu , citizen of Gursar , built the temple of Ninĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001021.7",
      "line_range": "7",
      "translation": "(Upper Text, 7) He built the Abzu-banda ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001021.9",
      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(Upper Text, 9) He built the temple of Nanše ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001021.11",
      "line_range": "11",
      "translation": "(Lower Text, 1) Ur-Nanše , king of Lagaš , established control of the Dilmun-boats ( coming ) from the foreign countries ."
